comment: Smooth as Tennessee Whiskey... must try!

It was actually released at the distillery in October 2017.  

Exceptional 100% rye with complex flavors.  If you like rye whiskey, try to find this one.
Pretty damned good. I’ll buy it again.
incredibly smooth for a rye with just enough sweet. nice fruit and walnut notes.
Sweet. Carmelly for a rye. Very nice nose and complex.
The average of 9 tasters has rated this. 4.9. It’s interesting and flavorful but, that’s a bit too optimistic. I’m rating it a 3.9.
